properties.name: cas.client.filter.processes-url
properties.description: Relative url to be processed by CasAuthenticationFilter for authentication.

properties.name: cas.client.filter.proxy-receptor-url
properties.description: Relative url to be processed by CasAuthenticationFilter for respond to proxy request from server.

properties.name: cas.client.filter.proxy-callback-url
properties.description: Absolute url of proxy callback. Must be equal to absolute url of ${cas.client.filter.proxy-receptor-url}. It will be passed to cas server as 'pgtUrl' parameter.

properties.name: cas.server.login-url
properties.description: Url for cas server login service.

properties.name: service.url
properties.description: Url of current service. It will be passed to cas server as 'service' parameter.
